title: Pink Floyd - From The Vault VI 2016 CDRip 320 [Bubanee]
description:
Note from the people involved:

Unlike previous releases in the set, From The Vault VI does not contain any of the rare sought after mixes, remixes or does it contain any material actually used. (Different Masters)
What makes this collection unique is that each track on this set are from original releases i.e Money/Brain Damage/Eclispe/Time
are all taken from the same source as the Japanese triangle release. No remastering or mixing done at all, what you get with this
collection is how Pink Floyd should sound, so this makes great for this collection of tracks.
Track 13: yes it's the double acoustic version and a version that was hidden away for years, enough said.
